Class Zombies

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.template.elements.Zombies

  • public class Zombies
extends java.lang.Object
    This class controls zombies entrance and their movement, makes list of zombies which are in the game.

      • findCells

        public void findCells(java.util.HashMap<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.String> info)
        Sets zombies line by line. If row is empty or has squash normal zombie will enter, if peashooters are more than other flowers bucket head zombie will enter, otherwise if other flowers are more than peashooters cone head zombie will enter.
        Parameters:
        info - as information of flowers in the playground
